---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section id="about" class="py-64 bg-[#fcfcfc] border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.3em] text-[#3aa693] font-bold uppercase mb-4">
        04 — About
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
        About Me
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8 font-light">
        A last-year student at the Hanoi University of Mining and Geology, I combine academic rigor 
        with 2 years of practical internship experience. Based in Hanoi, I am currently focused on 
        developing high-performance backend systems and specialized synchronization tools.
      </p>
      
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-light">
        My unique expertise lies at the intersection of traditional backend engineering and BIM 
        Integration and Game coding.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>